com.jdon.util

类 ObjectCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jdon.util.ObjectCreator

  • public final class ObjectCreator
extends Object
    Creates instance of any object, given its full qualified class name is given and it has event public accessable constructor. This class is event static class it can not be instantiated
    作者:
    Nadia Nashi
